name: Text
key: text
content-length: 686

<p>This class is intended to act as a base class for when defining custom controller renderings. It provides several useful properties that make the support features around setting component properties.&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Item property</h3>
<div>
<p>When a DataSource has been set on a controller the item property will return the item pointed to by the DataSource, otherwise the Item property will return the context Item.</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>PageItem property</h3>
<div>
<p>The PageItem property will always return the context Item.</p>
</div>
<h3>Parameters property</h3>
<p>Adds a Parameters property which returns a NameValueCollection of the parameters passed to the rendering.</p>
</div>
